snippet.title: A.O.T. 2 - STORY TRAILER
snippet.description:
GET READY FOR A SEQUEL OF COLOSSAL PROPORTIONS! A.O.T. 2 IS COMING ON THE 20TH MARCH 2018!

A.O.T. 2 is the sequel to the hugely successful ‘A.O.T. WINGS OF FREEDOM’, the titanic action game based on the worldwide anime series phenomenon, ‘Attack on Titan’.

A.O.T. 2 Official site:
http://www.koeitecmoeurope.com/aot2/
